list_of_files_in_comm_use_subset = os.listdir()

for i in tqdm(list_of_files_in_comm_use_subset):
    with open(i, "rb") as f:
        s = json.load(f)
    if len(s['abstract']) != 0:
        list_of_abstracts.append(s['abstract'][0]['text'])
        entire_body = ""
        for j in s['body_text']:
            entire_body += j['text'] + "\n\n"  
        list_of_body.append(entire_body)
